</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>興宗即位<pc>，</pc>以興平公主下嫁李元昊<pc>，</pc>以元昊為<term>駙馬都尉</term>
<pc>。</pc>重熙元年<pc>，</pc>夏國遣使來賀<pc>。</pc>李德昭薨<pc>，</pc>冊其子夏國公元昊為王<pc>。</pc>
<measure quantity="2" unit="years">
<num value="2">二</num>年</measure>
<pc>，</pc>來貢<pc>。</pc>
<measure quantity="12" unit="months">
