<pc>，</pc>宋遣郭禎以伐夏來報<pc>。</pc>
<measure quantity="10" unit="years">
<num value="10">十</num>年</measure>
<pc>，</pc>夏國獻所俘宋將及生口<pc>。</pc>
<measure quantity="11" unit="years">
<num value="11">十一</num>年</measure>
<pc>，</pc>遣使問<date notBefore="9999" notAfter="9999">宋</date>興師伐夏之由<pc>。</pc>
<measure quantity="12" unit="months">
<num value="12">十二</num>月</measure>
<pc>，</pc>禁吐渾鬻馬於夏<pc>，</pc>沿邊築障塞以防之<pc>。</pc>
<measure quantity="12" unit="years">
<num value="12">十二</num>年</measure>
<measure quantity="1" unit="month">
<num value="1">正</num>月</measure>
<pc>，</pc>遣同知析津府事耶律敵烈<pc>、</pc>樞密都承旨王惟吉諭夏國與宋和<pc>。</pc>
<measure quantity="2" unit="months">
<num value="2">二</num>月</measure>
<pc>，</pc>元昊以加上尊號<pc>，</pc>遣使來賀<pc>。</pc>耶律敵烈等使夏國還<pc>，</pc>奏元昊罷兵<pc>，</pc>遣使報宋<pc>。</pc>
